---
// Slide 6: Creative Units (3 Divisions)
---

<div class="slide-frame inactive w-full" id="slide-6" data-slide="5">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <span class="text-sm font-bold text-neonIndigo uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">
        06 // Division Scope
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-outfit text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
        Creative Units
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-slate-400 max-w-xl">
        Program kolaborasi ini didukung penuh oleh 3 sub-divisi utama
        penunjang transformasi digital:
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Unit 1: Web Development -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 hover-lift glow-lime">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg bg-neonLime/10 text-neonLime flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4 font-bold">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-outfit font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">
          Web Development
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-neonLime text-xs"></i>
            Landing page campaign
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-neonLime text-xs"></i>
            Microsite event
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-neonLime text-xs"></i>
            Company profile website
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-neonLime text-xs"></i>
            Integrasi sistem sederhana
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Unit 2: Graphic Design -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 hover-lift glow-indigo">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg bg-neonIndigo/10 text-neonIndigo flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4 font-bold">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-palette"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-outfit font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">
          Graphic Design
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-neonIndigo text-xs"></i>
            Pengembangan branding visual
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-neonIndigo text-xs"></i>
            Campaign design &amp; promotion
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-neonIndigo text-xs"></i>
            Social media content production
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-neonIndigo text-xs"></i>
            Event publication asset
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Unit 3: Photography -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 hover-lift glow-coral">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg bg-neonCoral/10 text-neonCoral flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4 font-bold">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-camera"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-outfit font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">
          Photography
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-neonCoral text-xs"></i>
            Dokumentasi event &amp; destinasi
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-neonCoral text-xs"></i>
            Visual asset production
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-neonCoral text-xs"></i>
            Photo library untuk kebutuhan industri
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
